%h1 Blog Posts

- @posts.each do |post|


  %h1= link_to post.title, comfy_blog_post_path(@cms_site.path, @blog.path, post.slug)
  .author
    = post.author
  .date
    = post.published_at.to_s(:db)
  .excerpt
    = post.excerpt.html_safe
  %h6= link_to ("Read More"), comfy_blog_post_path(@cms_site.path, @blog.path, post.slug), class: "btn btn-primary"
  <hr>  
  
= paginate @posts



























